WEBVTT

00:00.031 --> 00:03.297
<i>Previously on AMC's Better Call Saul...</i>

00:03.352 --> 00:05.032
Should I settle?

00:05.344 --> 00:09.140
_

00:11.415 --> 00:12.880
Hector Salamanca.

00:13.008 --> 00:15.281
- Turn the lights on.
- I'm back to normal.

00:15.283 --> 00:17.421
You'd rather tear down HHM than retire.

00:17.424 --> 00:20.008
You think I'm trouble now?
Imagine me as your enemy.

00:20.010 --> 00:22.289
It's a new client, and if I
mess this up, it's a <i> former</i> client.

00:22.291 --> 00:25.609
Sandpiper is settling. This is
the solution to everything!

00:25.611 --> 00:27.398
I'll be back in a few hours.

00:32.797 --> 00:36.067
"It was very still
except for the tree-toads

00:36.100 --> 00:40.405
and the frogs in the brook
peeping mournfully,

00:40.437 --> 00:42.607
and every little while

00:42.639 --> 00:45.343
Mabel could hear strange
rustlings in the leaves.

00:45.375 --> 00:48.312
She tried to remember the way home,

00:48.346 --> 00:50.448
but the woods looked so different now

00:50.480 --> 00:53.550
that she couldn't think which way to go.

00:53.584 --> 00:56.053
She began to be frightened.

00:56.087 --> 00:57.922
'What's that?' said Mabel.

00:57.954 --> 01:00.524
'Oh, I'm... I'm so frightened!'

01:00.558 --> 01:03.560
In a minute or two she
heard the howl again...

01:03.593 --> 01:06.864
'O-o-o-w!'...

01:06.897 --> 01:10.101
a long, wild cry.

01:10.133 --> 01:14.604
She began to run, but the
poor thing had lost her way."

01:14.638 --> 01:16.940
Is she gonna be okay?

01:16.974 --> 01:19.811
- She'll be fine, Jimmy.
- How do you know?

01:19.843 --> 01:22.946
Just listen. You'll see.

01:25.715 --> 01:27.718
"It was so dark that she stumbled

01:27.751 --> 01:29.920
over the bushes and the
roots of the trees..."

